{"about_the_game":"Step into the spooky world of Shadows Are Alive, where relentless suspense meets an ever-evolving survival horror. As the mansion's walls shift and secrets unravel, can you keep your wits about you?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554930/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif.gif?t=1730742826\" /><br><br>Imagine: Teaming up with your friends for an adventure, <strong>you're a group of childhood heroes, exploring various locations and discovering danger.  From a haunted mansion to a spooky carnival, unpredictable at every corner</strong>. But this isn't your typical hide-and-seek. <strong>Channel the powers of your alter egos</strong>.  Whether that's a heroic <strong>firefighter</strong>, mastermind <strong>lockpicker</strong>, insightful <strong>psychologist</strong>, or the resourceful <strong>inventor</strong>. Pull on their abilities to survive the night.  What's the catch? The dark entity known as <strong>&quot;The Shift&quot;</strong> is on your tail as you try to find your way out, and this entity plays for keeps.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554930/extras/saaD2.png?t=1730742826\" /><br><br>Every turn unveils new challenges, every strategy you devise is put to the test. Keep your lantern close, it's your line of defense against The Shift's eerie &quot;<strong>Shift Vision</strong>&quot;. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554930/extras/Screenshot_2024-08-12_19-07-10.png?t=1730742826\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554930/extras/Screenshot_2024-02-19_20-33-02.png?t=1730742826\" /><br><br>Will you escape the cluthes of the Shift or fall to his wrath?  More maps are coming to prepare to get spooky!<br><br><strong>Game Highlights:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Evolving Playgrounds: Randomly generated maps creates fresh thrills on every play-through, challenges, and pathways.<br></li><li>Aura or Nothing: Evade The Shift who's after your glow \u2013 the very aura that defines you in this shadow-filled world.<br></li><li>Vivid Imagery: A game world bursting with color and character\u2014imagine if your favorite animated movie met the coolest survival game.<br></li><li>Shape-Shifting Pursuer: The Shift isn't just any foe; navigate their dual forms, both the tangible terror and its swift, smoke-like state.<br></li><li>Epic Team-Ups: Join forces, mix and match abilities, and strategize with friends in high-octane multiplayer sessions.<br></li><li>Hidden Depths: Behind each alter ego, lies a tale waiting to be uncovered. And The Shift? Its past is shrouded in mystery.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554930/extras/FirefighterAndShift.png?t=1730742826\" /><br><br>Shadows Are Alive promises a thrilling ride that's packed with adrenaline, strategy, and mystery. So, ready for a heart-racing, time-chasing, and mind-blowing adventure?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Shadows Owner Badge","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2554930/7962372a7a7f4940307da16ce4cb51878603f15d.jpg"},{"name":"Boo Buster Membership","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2554930/a503105a176b671e3714fcda73237f4aea6deb01.jpg"},{"name":"First Hero Win","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2554930/a2c61924bb68433d93f961ea4c9d67f1ca411778.jpg"},{"name":"GOAT Ghost Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2554930/104054dd0bf56abdc1e20fa58bc6c51794f7da4b.jpg"},{"name":"Easter Eggs Galore","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2554930/8e55990919c4c250d49d6df9994919783f34023c.jpg"},{"name"